# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0.0] - 2021-09-10
### Added
- Add "prune" command which cleanes all node_modules folder under the current working directory
- Add "init" command to quickly create a config file with some default rules


## [Unreleased]
### Added
- Add additional patterns for new config files
### Changed
- Reworked the *init* command to use pattern groups for config file creation
